		<p>All it requires is proper planning, where we explore various layout options to choose the best one. Optimal use of natural light can be made by adding sky lights to brighten up the space, while a portable or permanent staircase makes it easy to access. Our design and planning team works closely with our clients, paying attention to every detail and preference you have and make the best effort to incorporate it in the design. </p>
